'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 5''' is the fifth issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 3|''Star Wars'' (1977) 3]] {{C|Part 1}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Unknown Worlds of Science Fiction Vol 1 2|War Toy]]" {{C|Part 2}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Marvel Preview Vol 1 4|The Sword in the Star!: Stave 1: Alas, the Seeds of Man!]]" {{C|Part 1}}

*Competition to win one of twenty-five sets of ''Star Wars'' figures from Palitoy. To enter, readers must answer six questions. Notably, the [[Star Wars Weekly 4|previous issue]] stated the prize would be a copy of ''[[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|Star Wars]]'' on 8mm film.

